(51, 'Nutrition', 'nutrition', '', '<div><table border="0" cellpadding="0" width="750"> <tbody><tr> <td class="style4" width="50" valign="top" style="height: 200px"> <p class="style1" align="left"><strong>DIET</strong><br />  “It''s just not diet!” </p>                               <p align="left"><img src="images/stories/nutrition1-1.jpg" border="0" align="left" /></p>                            <p align="left">&nbsp;</p></td>                           <td class="style4" colspan="2" valign="middle" style="height: 200px"><p class="style1" align="left"><span class="style4">There are many  considerations that must be addressed before embarking on a balanced life.</span><br />                             </p>                          </td>                         </tr>                         <tr>                           <td class="style4" colspan="3" valign="top"><div align="justify"><span class="style1"><strong>METABOLIC TYPE                             </strong><br /> The Maxim Longevity and Research Institute diet program is geared to each individual. Factors such as, Metabolic Type, (the metabolism and fat burning and storage process), of each individual can be dramatically different. Many people have been in frustrating situations of seeing their friends and colleagues, eating whatever they want and staying skinny or thin, while they become fat and obese. There are clinical, factual definitions that explain the process and why this happens. Here at Maxim Longevity and Research Institute, we understand this process. <br />                             <br />                           </span></div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr>                           <td class="style4" colspan="3" valign="top"><div class="style1" align="justify"><strong>BODY TYPE </strong><br /> Everyone has a different body type. There are 3 distinct body types, Endomorph, Mesomorph and Ectomorph, each has different combinations between them. (see the picture) </div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"> </td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td class="style4" valign="middle"><div align="center"><strong>ENDOMORPH</strong><br />                             <br />  <img src="images/stories/endo.jpg" border="0" align="left" /></div></td>                           <td colspan="2" valign="top"><div class="style4" align="justify"><br />                               <span class="style1">The characteristics of a Endormorph are as follows. Endomorphs resemble a pear or apple shape with a medium to larger bone structure. Endomorphs have a tendency to gain weight and store fat easily. This body type has a genetic propensity to become obese even when consuming very little calories and working out at a moderate level. <br /> This body type has the slowest of all the metabolisms and has the highest incidence for diabetes, cardiovascular disease, allergies, obesity and many more. This is because of the slow metabolizing of fat, proteins and carbohydrates that lead to an acidic state in the body. Endomorphs have average to poor cardiovascular fitness and average to above average ability to put on muscle and unusual strength. The majority of type II diabetics are Endomorphs therefore, they MUST watch what they eat in addition to proper exercise and not just walking. Usually, we must stimulate an endomorphs hormonal axis and thyroid activity to boost the, already, suppressed organs from doing their proper job properly. After making a few adjustments from clinical testing (see information guide) the Maxim Longevity and Research Institute Coach or practitioner can give the patient the proper substrates to insure the, highest and best, result in the shortest period of time. </span></div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" height="47" valign="top"> </td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td align="left" valign="middle"><div align="center"><strong class="style4">MESOMORPH <br />                             </strong><br />                             <img src="images/stories/meso.jpg" border="0" align="left" /><br />  </div></td>                           <td colspan="2" valign="top"><div class="style4" align="justify"><br />                               <span class="style1">The characteristics of a Mesormorph body type are as follows. Mesomorphs are broad shouldered, well built people who have medium bone structures. They have an innate ability to put on lean muscle. These body types display the best results when put on a guided approach. This body type has a medium to fast metabolism and a much lower incidence of degenerative diseases due higher metabolic action. This body type you need to watch out for because of possible blood sugar, insulin instability and the problem of the body eating lean muscle tissue and staying acidic. The Maxim Longevity and Research Institute Coaching staff has customized eating and supplementation plans based on hormonal, insulinic, adrenal and training protocols for maximum results. </span></div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" height="53" valign="top"> </td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td valign="middle"><div align="center"><strong class="style4">ECTOMORPH</strong><br />                               <br />                             <img src="images/stories/ecto.jpg" border="0" align="left" /><br />                           </div></td>                           <td colspan="2" valign="top"><div class="style4" align="justify"><br />                               <span class="style1">The characteristics of an Ectomorph is as follows. Ectomorphs are primarily thin, lanky people with a smaller bone structure, with narrow waistlines and shoulder widths, at least years ago. These body types have extraordinary metabolisms and can break down glucose (carbs) at an amazing rate. These are the people that can sit next to you eating pizza and pasta and loose weight and you just look at it and gain weight. The idea for every body type is to get it processing like an ectomorph for the fat burning ability. Ectomorphs, unfortunately, have a very difficult time with muscle wasting and must be counseled on the balancing of dietary considerations to prevent hypoglycemia, as well as, high pH levels because of the body utilizing lean muscle as an energy source instead of fat. </span></div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"><br />                           <br /></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"><div class="style1" align="justify"><strong class="style4">GENETIC PRE-DISPOSITION </strong><br /> Every individual is born into this life with different genetic triggers. Your Great Grandparents and beyond have set the stage for your genetic pathway in your current life. Disease states, fat cell storage and sizes, hormonal pathways and every endocrine, immune function limitation and stability is pre determined at your time of birth. Whether of not, you support the good that you received from your genetics or fighting against it is another story. My theory is that we may have received some good genes or bad ones. The idea is that you make your body as healthy as you can, <strong>NOT </strong>to trigger the bad genes. We all have family that has, diabetes, cancer, heart disease, skin conditions, hair loss etc. The last thing we want to do is <strong>TRIGGER </strong>these conditions. So, the goal is at Maxim Longevity and Research Institute is to reverse those disease states or support all your organs so you never have to deal with your <strong>BAD </strong>genetic issues and make your immune system  consistent and strong! </div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"><br />                           <br /></td>                         </tr>                         <tr>                           <td class="style4" valign="middle"><img src="images/stories/bloodtype.jpg" border="0" align="left" /></td>                           <td class="style4" width="3" valign="top"> </td>                       <td valign="top"><div class="style4" align="justify"><strong>BLOOD TYPES</strong><br />                                 <span class="style1"><strong>“I Wouldn''t have believed it if I didn''t witness it myself!” </strong><br /> Eight years ago I was introduced to the blood type diet. This dietary consideration customizes your foods depending on your blood type. The premise is that every food is broken down into an amino acid so it can enter into your blood stream and fuel the muscle that burns the calories that burns fat. Certain foods from generations were indigenous to their culture like, Spanish, rice and beans. Irish, fruits, veggies, fish. Indians, buffalo and grains etc. Each one of these groupings had genetic adaptations that allowed them to digest, assimilate and properly eliminate for proper longevity and health.</span> </div></td>                         </tr>                                                    <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"><br />                           <br /></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td class="style4" colspan="3" valign="top"><div align="justify"><span class="style1">Today, at Maxim Longevity and Research Institute we have worked with individuals with allergic reactions to certain foods and qualified it through extensive allergy testing with food extracts and blood tests. This unique discovery coupled with dramatic revisions because of plant sterols, phytoestrogens and clinical group analysis has proven to be a tremendous success within the Maxim Longevity and Research Institute. Get your custom Maxim Longevity and Research Institute blood type diet plan from your Maxim Longevity and Research Institute  Coach or practitioner. </span><br />     </div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"><div align="justify"><span class="style4"><br />                                 <strong>INSULIN</strong><br />                           </span><span class="style1">The body''s master hormone. This hormone is one of the most misunderstood and compromised hormones we have ever seen in clinical and historical review. This hormone is basically responsible for the direction your calories go, no matter how many you eat or don''t eat. Either your calories are stored in fat cells as fat or the liver as glycogen to make energy and burn fat. Unless you master this action, why waste your time? A simple saliva test will show whether or not you have a problem and we have the answers to fix it. Remember, you must preserve the basic function. You must feed muscle because muscle burns the calories that burn fat and create energy for optimal health.</span> <br />   </div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr>                           <td class="style4" valign="top"><p align="justify"><strong><br />                               <br />                             BOWEL HEALTH</strong><br />                             </p>                           <p align="justify"><img src="images/stories/nutritiongirl.jpg" border="0" align="left" /></p></td>                           <td class="style4" valign="top"> </td>                           <td class="style4" valign="top"><p align="justify">&nbsp;</p>                             <ol><li>                                 <div align="justify"><span class="style1">Most Americans have IBS or irritable bowel syndrome. IBS is basically an unhealthy bowel state. When you were an infant you used to have perfect bowels in most cases, a bowel movement after each meal. Most Americans don''t do this and therefore have moderate to severe complications. Good bowel health tells the story. The story of the body digesting, assimilating and eliminating the garbage from the foods you just ate. Unfortunately, clinical evidencing has seen undigested matter recognizable from many years ago, all stored in the mucous and fecal decay attached to the intestinal and colon lining. People should NOT have any fat exceeding the belt line. This means, in most cases, either high body fat or intestinal distention. Usually, it is a bit of both. I have said time and time again that doing a good digestive and intestinal detox is the cornerstone of health.</span></div>                               </li><li class="style1">                                 <div align="justify">Of equal importance, 99% of the chemicals (neurotransmitters such as serotonin) that determine your mood are made in the intestinal tract from the food you eat, and only 1% of them are made in your brain. </div>                               </li><li class="style1">                                 <div align="justify">So if your intestinal tract is inflamed and unable to function normally, you may not be able to make enough of these chemicals to keep your moods stable.</div>                               </li></ol></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"><span class="style4">                            </span>                           <div class="style1" align="justify">Literally, I call it cheating because, all you have to do once you see your gut growing is take some detox capsules and viola! It disappears. Why I have to convince people today about its importance is ridiculous. If you want to be lean and healthy just detox and cleanse the intestines and colon. It is simple, painless and the single most dramatic success I have ever seen. (see illustration of intestinal digestive process</div></td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"> </td>                         </tr>                         <tr class="style4">                           <td colspan="3" valign="top"> </td>                         </tr>                         <tr>                           <td class="style4" colspan="3" valign="top"><p align="justify">  <br />   <span class="style1"><strong>TIME</strong><br /> I don''t know about some of you but I surely don''t like to take the time to exercise and not get the best result in the shortest period of time. It is very important to both train according to your genetics with specific muscle fiber types that respond differently to different forms of exercise techniques. If you train wrong your result is negligible. That is why so many people fail. I don''t blame them. We at Maxim Longevity and Research Institute make sure that 1. you are fueled properly from your eating plan. 2. you are fueled properly before, during and after your exercise and that you are hormonally balanced, adrenal balanced, insulin stable, to make certain you gained the greatest benefit in the shortest period of time. Time is money, so make the best of it! <br />     <br />   <strong>AGE</strong> <br /> This is one subject that really bothers me. If I hear one more time that it is my age that is why I am: tired, fat, wrinkly, have no muscle or I look pretty good for my age considering the other people I am going to scream! My father always said to me that they are putting people on the moon their must be an answer. There is! Balance your diet, detox from the environmental toxins and rebalance your hormones, that is the answer. How you do it is another story. That is the reason for the discovery and the creation of the Maxim Longevity and Research Institute program. Everyone has the same opportunities to achieve anti-aging or healthy benefits from this program. We consistently, take10, 20 even 30 years of aging signs from people that are devoted to the program. We have hundreds of pictures and testimonials to prove the successes. <br />     <br />   <strong>EXERCISE</strong> <br /> This is where I get in trouble with most trainers. Exercise, without balancing the body is basically, a waste of time. It is like planning to go on a long trip without putting fuel in the tank. Think about it. If you don''t eat right to fuel your glycogen or energy stores for training, or have a toxic digestive and intestinal system that does not allow for proper nutrient absorbsion or have a hormonal pattern that is upside down or that of a 100 year old, why bother? That is like ‘putting the cart before the horse.'' I hate to say it, but here it goes, we have been consistently successful in clients loosing over 20 to 30 pounds of fat, without exercising at all! Why, because in most cases, they have been starving themselves of proper nutrient intake and absorbsion. <br />                             Now let me clarify by  saying that, of course exercise is important, but not stand alone. <br />     <br /> It is a standing anomaly in the offices and amongst clients at the Maxim Longevity and Research Institute Center that I can maintain a 4 to 5% Body Fat percentage without crazy cardio training or weight training with terrible genetics. I literally, took 5 months off from any exercise in the gym and still maintained an incredible body fat percentage. Why? It is all about balance. That is what we teach at the centers. <br />     <br />   <strong>OVERVIEW</strong> <br />                             In short, it important  to note that is not usually the person that <strong>fails to succeed </strong>but the  person that <strong>fails to obtain balance </strong>. Balance of internal health,  hormonal health and proper diagnostics insures a fantastic, dynamic and  lifetime result. </span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><!--Session data--> </div><!--Session data--><!--Session data--><!--Session data-->', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2009-04-13 09:27:00', 62, '', '2014-03-28 11:47:39', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-04-13 09:27:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 19, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 648, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(52, 'Managed Program', 'managed-program', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p><table border="0" width="750" style="text-align: center"><tbody><tr><td> <strong style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.3em">Maxim Body System</strong><p style="font-size: 14px" align="center"><strong><a href="javascript:Void(0)">Managed Program</a></strong></p><p style="text-align: left; font-size: 14px" align="left">Maxim Longevity and Research Institute has designed a comprehensive interactive <span style="line-height: 1.3em">software program to work with our experienced Maxim Coaching Staff and guiding the patient through </span><span style="line-height: 1.3em">the process of ultimate health.</span></p><p style="text-align: left; font-size: 14px" align="left">This proprietary wellness program integrates diagnostics, therapeutics, nutrition, detoxing, <span style="line-height: 1.3em">hormone balancing and exercise into an customized, individualized wellness program.</span></p><p style="text-align: left; font-size: 14px" align="left">The program ultimately changes the patient''s internal environment to reflect total health, <span style="line-height: 1.3em">inside and out.</span></p><p style="text-align: left; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.807999610900879px"><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal">Maxim’s trained staff has taken thousands of people successfully through </span><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal">this proven process developed over 8 years with coordination between </span><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal">doctor’s offices and our training team.</span> </p></td><td><a href="javascript:void(0)"><img src="images/managedpro.jpg" border="1" alt="Managed Program" width="300" height="212" /></a> </td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-align: center"