(71, 'Symptom Solver', 'symptom-solver', '', 'Cleansing is some of the deepest work we can do for ourselves; bringing the body from a toxic state to a state of total wellness and rejuvenation is not an easy task. You are taking on a huge project that, with patience, will leave you feeling better than you could ever imagine. Over more than 10 years Maxim Body Systems have tested different methods to find the most gentle and simple way for you to incorporate cleansing into your busy life. This does not mean that you will go through this program without any side effects because, chances are, you will. Both long and short term neglect of your body results in toxin build-up. As one becomes accustomed to living in a toxic state, feeling badly becomes normal and feeling great is a thing of the past. Cleanses bring that toxicity to the surface and as it is flushed from the body it is common to feel some discomfort. The more toxic you are the more sick you might feel; follow your diet and protocol guidelines as we set them for you and the effects will be as minimal as possible. Just give it time, feelings of discomfort will pass as you are on your way to total rejuvenation and health.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:20:17', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:20:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 34, '', '', 0, 731, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(72, 'Loose Stools', 'loose-stools', '', 'If you encounter loose stools it could be because your body is not absorbing enough water.  You can counteract these effects by taking Toxin Clear or charcoal.  Toxin Clear will both absorb some of the toxins your body is releasing and also help eliminate the loose stools.  You can take more fiber supplements, Rice Bran, Rice Bran Chia Blend, and or vegetables from your Blood Type foods list: like spinach, zucchini, chard and cucumbers.  Cucumbers will also help to regulate your pH.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:24:23', 62, '', '2009-08-07 11:27:16', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:24:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 33, '', '', 0, 97, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(73, 'Headache', 'headache', '', 'If your headache is too painful, slow down the detox.  Avoid taking any painkillers or over the counter medication because the idea with this process is to experience the detox.  If you numb yourself with painkillers you will not know what your body is doing.  Also, why replace more toxins into your body when you are trying to flush them out?  Try taking half of the protocol for a day or two this should relieve your symptoms.  Toxin Clear, if you are not constipated, will help to absorb the die-off of toxins in your body and reduce the headache.  Make sure to drink plenty of water.  If you are dehydrated the dehydration will definitely add to a headache.  The best methods is to drink approximately half your body weight in oz. of water a day with some electrolytes. ', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:27:31', 62, '', '2009-08-07 14:23:02', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:27:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 32, '', '', 0, 101, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(74, 'Stomachache or Lack of Energy', 'stomachache-or-lack-of-energy', '', 'You might not be going to the bathroom enough.  Try slowing down the fiber.  Make sure you are Ph is balanced acidity can cause slow bowels and a stomach ache.  You should be checking your pH three times a day.  Make sure you are eating according to your blood type and not eating any sugar or refined foods.  If you are eating bread or processed foods you will have a stomach ache and feel lethargic.  If you are drinking soda you will get a stomach ache stick to water and green tea without sugar.  To increase energy drink Green Tea and take Aminoplex with Stimulant.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:29:57', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:29:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 31, '', '', 0, 126, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(75, 'Headache', 'headache-yeast', '', 'Yeast is "dying off" and it is not uncommon for you to experience headaches.  Take toxin clear to absorb the toxins that are being released as the yeast “dies”.  If your headache becomes too severe slow down the detox.  Excessive overgrowth may be too rampant especially if you took too many antibiotics in the past.  In this case you might want a prescription antifungal (Diflucan) can be prescribed by the doctors office.  Also, eliminating drug use during this cleanse is essential to reducing headache and your well-being.  If you choose to continue alcohol and drug use this cleanse will not work.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:42:50', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:42:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 30, '', '', 0, 80, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(76, 'Born Umbilicus - Heavy Metal', 'born-umbilicus-heavy-metal', '', 'Before birth, your umbilical cord is what supplies nutrients to you from the placenta. If the mother is highly toxic, the baby will also be highly toxic.  Also, anything the mother consumes (fluorinated water, etc.) will most likely transfer to the baby.  A baby’s organs are not all fully developed during this time and cannot process an overload of chemicals.  The body filters these out of the blood and whatever cannot be excreted is stored in the tissues.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:52:23', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 29, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(77, 'Heavy Metals - Dental', 'heavy-metals-dental', '', 'Mercury is found in the metal fillings in your mouth.  This toxic chemical is released slowly into your system over the years leading to chemical toxicity.<br />                 <br /> Heavy metals disrupt metabolic function in two basic ways: First, they accumulate, disrupting function in vital organs and glands such as the heart, brain, kidneys, bone, liver, etc.  Second, they displace vital nutritional minerals from where they should be in the body to provide biological function.  For example, enzymes are catalysts for virtually every biochemical reaction in all life-sustaining processes of metabolism.  When the body is toxic lead and cadmium replace the enzymes and calcium that should be driving your metabolic processes.  Toxic metals ca not fulfill the same role as the nutritional minerals. Thus, the presence of toxic chemicals becomes critically disruptive to enzyme activity.  Because their impact is at such a basic level, heavy metals can be causal factors in literally any health problem.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 11:58:45', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 11:58:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 28, '', '', 0, 0, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(78, 'Feeling Sick (Mild to Severe)', 'feeling-sick-mild-to-severe', '', 'Again, this is toxins leaving your body and it is important to make sure that your bowels are moving 2-3 times a day.  If not then take the intestinal cleanse part 1 and part 2 and mediate it yourself.  Usually, three months from the time you do the intestinal cleanse it is good to do the intestinal cleanse again you can talk to your coach about this or mediate it yourself.  If you have metal fillings or you were born with high levels of toxicity you might have a lot of health problems related to the metal and the cleanse is both important for eliminating these and regaining your health.  Slow down or stop the cleanse for a little bit.  If you have normal or loose bowels take some charcoal.  Also, do an additional 24 hour urine test, stool test or blood test to test your toxicity.   <br />', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 12:02:21', 62, '', '2009-08-07 14:00:58', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 12:02:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 27, '', '', 0, 102, 'robots=\nauthor='),
