(94, 'Loose Stools', 'loose-stools', '', 'Occasionally, bowel pockets or parasite die-off may cause some diarrhea or watery stools.  These should firm up with an increase of fiber supplements or vegetables such as spinach or broccoli.  Refer to you eating for your blood type guide for beneficial vegetables.  Make sure your mineral densities are good to provide a proper stool.  Use Angstrom minerals on an empty stomach twice a day and Check your pH 2-3 times a day.  Recommendation is to read the label for customized dosage.  If the bowels do not regain form within a couple of days under normal diet guidelines set by the program then reduce the dosage of parasite cleanse until normalized bowels are maintained.  You may go 10 days on the cleanse and 1 week off if necessary to mediate bowels.  It is essential that you remain consistent while doing this cleanse.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 12:33:55', 62, '', '2009-08-10 09:34:49', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 12:33:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 12, '', '', 0, 87, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(95, 'Bloating', 'bloating', '', 'Charcoal will help absorb the toxins that cause bloating during the die-off of parasites. Another option is MSM.  MSM is an organic sulfur compound.  It is contained naturally in food, or it should be, but often it disappears or is significantly reduced because of over processing.  MSM has proven to be a very effective treatment for parasites.   Taking MSM will increase the rate of die off and removal of parasites.  Also, you can increase the amount of part 2.  Part 2 contains Betaine hydrochloride and is a non-essential nutrient and a source of hydrochloric acid, a naturally occurring chemical in the stomach that helps digest food by breaking up fats and proteins.', '', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2009-08-07 12:35:33', 62, '', '2009-08-10 09:35:42', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2009-08-07 12:35:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 103, 'robots=\nauthor=');
