(27, 1, 0, '01323400015 (45)', '', '<h3 class="StaffNameText">                                    Alkalizer</h3>                                <p class="descript">                                    <strong>Body pH refers to the degree of acidity</strong> (sourness) or alkalinity                                    (bitterness) of the body''s blood or other fluids. Acidity is expressed on the pH                                    scale, in which 1.0 is a very low pH and strongly acid, 7.0 is neutral, and above                                    7.0 is alkaline, with a high pH limit of 14. Blood is normally slightly alkaline,                                    with a pH range of 7.35 to 7.45. The blood''s acid-alkalinity balance is controlled                                    precisely because even a minor deviation from the normal range can severely affect                                    many organs.                                </p>                                <p class="descript">                                    All cells, organs and fluids in the body have their own preferred pH values in order                                    to operate at peak performance. These ranges are usually found in the slightly alkaline                                    level. When the pH is pushed higher or lower than the level preferred, the ability                                    of the fluid or cell to do its job is "stressed." It cannot utilize the nutrients                                    it needs, eliminate the wastes collected, etc., until the proper pH is restored.                                    This is where you, the master operator of your body, can make things right using                                    pH testing on a regular basis.                                </p>                                <p class="descript">                                    It is said that the root of all disease starts in an acidic environment. Alkalizer                                    is your cornerstone product to regulate the body’s homeostatic pH levels.</p>                                <p class="descript">                                    The importance of alkalization is well documented. Over 75 ionic & angstrom                                    minerals combined with over 30 metabolic enzymes, over 15 amino-acids, electrolytes,                                    dissolved oxygen & hydrogen. This product supports the integrity of your pH                                    balance, enhance energy levels, immune system balance, breathing, allergy relief,                                    free-radical removal, nutrient absorption, removal of lactic acid and uric acid.                                    It generates & delivers oxygen in the body as needed. All of this with a delivery                                    system that delivers it into each cell.                                    <br />                                    It is said that,<strong> “Cancer can’t survive in an alkaline environment.”</strong></p>                                <p class="descript">                                    <strong>Suggestions for Use:</strong></p>                                <p class="descript">                                    1 oz dropper-top bottle. Clear liquid with slight lemon taste. 12 drops morning                                    & evening in any liquid. ALKALIZER produces no free radicals.</p>                                <p class="descript">                                    For extreme diseases: Take 30 drops morning and evening with 4 or more oz. of liquid.                                    Check with your Maxim Health Coach for details.</p>                                <p class="descript">                                    For Best Results: Take with Maxim Meal 2 to 3 times per day to achieve alkalinity.                                    Check 3 times or more per day for average pH balance. Goal is 6.8 to 7.4 daily.</p>                                                                    <span class="descript">ALKALIZER formula contains: 80 minerals, 17 amino acids, electrolytes,                                        34 metabolic enzymes, oxygen and hydrogen. 1 Fluid ounce bottle of clear liquid.</span>                                    ', 'resized/Alkalizer_4a0a899438bd7_90x90.gif', 'Alkalizer_4a0a899449950.gif', 'N', 0.0000, 'pounds', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 'inches', '', -7, 1242190800, '3-5d.gif', 'N', 0, NULL, 1242204268, 1242207574, 'Alkalizer', 7, '', '', 0, 'piece', 0, 'N,N,N,N,N,Y,20%,10%,', 'none,0,0,1', '', '0,0'),
